Romanization

[Verse 1]
Jib-e deul-eogamyeon
Dochaghaessdago yeonlaghaneunge

Joh-ayo nuleul sigan-e
Meseji hwag-inhaneunge

Chinguyeodo jiltu naneunde
Seukinsib jom jajehaneunge

Geuge geuleohge eolyeobnya neon
Mwoga geuleohge eolyeobdago

Geunde jjalishae neul saelowo
You're the best
Jigyeobjido anh-a silhjiga anh-a

Neo nappeunde geugeo nado da aneunde
Nan wae ileolkka gwaenhi yeolbad-a
Jeonsaeng-e daeche mwon joeleul jyeossgillae

[Hook]
Daeche wae geuleoneun geoya nahante
Daeche mwoga munjen geoya malhae

