[Rap]
Neoneun seoulgugyeong gat-a
Mapo gangnam gwanghwamun
Jam-eseo kkaeeonaseo haneun jis-ilagon. neoui
Katog inseutageulaem. peiseubug-eul
Tueohaneun il. nan neoui salm-ui ilbubun-ui
Gwangwang-gaeg-in geos gat-a
Nan neowa incheon-ina gimpolo dangjang tteonago sip-eunde
Maeu seulpeun geon mal-a hyeonsil-eun mal-ya gibunman bungtteo issneunge daya
Geunde jjalishae neul saelowo
